      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NEEDLE AND SEAT (6) lines up chasing another win after getting around the 300m at this track in a sharp 16.86 on May 7. Rates a top chance again if runs up to latest. REMI NATH (8) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 10 lengths at this track in a handy 23.48. Draws out wide but likes the trip. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Will go close again if runs up to latest. NANNY'S BOY (1) was safely held last time finishing a 4 length sixth at this track (24.16) but back to the scene of his latest victory. Has a good record here at this journey. Has a strong record from this draw, notching three wins and two minor placings from five starts. Has the ability to give this a shake. SARILDA (2) is another with top-three prospects.",
